snippet.title: AIB
snippet.description: AIB provides inspiring and informative programming to feed your mind, body and spirit – from learning a new language to exploring new ideas.  We invite you to enjoy content that expands your horizons, stimulates thought, encourages creativity and motivates action.   A wealth of knowledge and enlightening entertainment are at your fingertips when you enjoy AIB programming!
